{"tid":2210104,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【錄埋出嚟Diu多次】既然黃絲咁鐘意互Diu 就等我Diu哂你地所有人2","createTime":"2020-09-20T07:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T02:14:36.000Z","uid":82955,"like":83,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"702178f76e3248b9ce5f770ee30cfb09c025787f","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"Sor我標題撚 其實喺好愛大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前見到有位Ching Post咗段文字Diu到大家飛起 <br />\n<blockquote>既然黃絲咁鐘意互屌,就等我屌哂你地所有人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2205098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2205098</a></blockquote><br />\n<strong>覺得都幾有道理同幾有能量拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以我加加減減內容再加入咗啲自己諗法 <br />\n仲走去錄埋出嚟 希望大家聽到又會感受深啲<br />\n唔鐘意聽我把聲嘅話 <strong><span class=\"gold\">你都要直飛片尾呀 片尾你會鐘意的<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4jKKcbL1pk \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB4jKKcbL1pk%20&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=a69c591d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B4jKKcbL1pk </a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFUCQrDlg7N/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFUCQrDlg7N%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=c8c73de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFUCQrDlg7N%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link&h=04c82bc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFUCQrDlg7N/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n雖然同連登文化唔是咁match<br />\n但都想講兩句提提大家<br />\n「<strong><span class=\"pink\">世界真的不是那麼美好 所以你必然要更努力保守你心 掙扎 愛你</span></strong>」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e86d6e125ae7bb2479b6804ff284e3665d485fb","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":16,"dislike":13,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得:<br />\n「齊上齊學」<br />\n「光復自己」<br />\n「Be Humble」<br />\n「革自己的命」<br />\n<br />\n憤恨中請你不要被黑暗吞噬<br />\n我知咁樣同連登仔 (我都係) 講好唔尋常呀<br />\n但我想講 你地就係黑暗中嘅果一點光<br />\n你地都鼓勵咗好多人好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係真架<br />\n掙扎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4f6037d3e545faf38ae7bc79b6241bd9504822","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"推 齊上齊學<br />\n推 光復自己<br />\n推 BE HUMBLE<br />\n推 革自己的命"},{"pid":"7e4d91cf0d019187f4b9a302e5403a9b225acc5c","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"推 齊上齊學"},{"pid":"b3cdc1549abd26eb79012c05692f0bf76c6ac435","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"推 光復自己"},{"pid":"ad364facf9fd131a4856600847730d99924294be","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"推 BE HUMBLE"},{"pid":"ef85013107842672bb6d35712555e29f02bf7a5c","tid":2210104,"uid":283912,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"你屌得好溫柔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69de7deae0455abc7871289a74f9fd549019f96","tid":2210104,"uid":82955,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:11:14.000Z","msg":"推 革自己的命"},{"pid":"b46090e35a32ad079b973d56722136ae8b0ab571","tid":2210104,"uid":129340,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"互屌多數係5毛\b，而且會係好低質咁屌